com.yworks.yfiles.view.input

Class QueryPositionHandlerEventArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.view.input.InputModeEventArgs
      • com.yworks.yfiles.view.input.QueryPositionHandlerEventArgs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEventArgs

    public class QueryPositionHandlerEventArgs
extends InputModeEventArgs
    Event argument that is used to query the IPositionHandler that is used to move the items while dragging via MoveInputMode.
    See Also:
    MoveInputMode, MoveInputMode.addQueryPositionHandlerListener(com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IEventHandler)
